{"tid":988553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大婚之日遭7男扒光亂親 新娘崩潰淚訴婚鬧慘狀","createTime":"2019-01-20T07:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T08:22:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8d3386dd34c95563574f0be92152e977c4f1621c","tid":988553,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:27:30.000Z","msg":"中國大陸頻傳低俗婚鬧事件，不少賓客假借「鬧洞房」、「熱鬧一下」的名義，對伴娘、新娘毛手毛腳，讓美好的大喜之日成了公然性騷擾現場。一名大陸網友近日發文，曝光多名新娘遭到婚鬧的慘痛經驗，呼籲新郎要懂得保護自己心愛的人。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸網友「一地金啊」撰文揭露多名新娘的慘痛婚鬧經驗，其中一名女子「白玉」和男友相戀 8 年終於修成正果，她和許多女孩一樣，嚮往一場有著鮮花、掌聲、祝福的體面婚禮，沒想到竟是一場惡夢。<br />\n<br />\n婚禮當天，白玉凌晨就起床梳妝，但上午 10 點她就被鎖死在新房裡，一群陌生男子闖進房裡把她壓在床上，還有人趁亂親她，甚至企圖扒下她的婚紗，白玉只能拼命用手護住胸前，淒厲地呼喚丈夫，但丈夫早就被親友拉去陪酒。最後，白玉被脫得一絲不掛，比起新娘，更像土匪搶來的女俘虜，而當白玉無助地在房裡被蹂躪時，長輩們卻在屋外直說「年輕人真會玩，這婚禮辦得好，熱鬧」，讓她備感羞辱、怨憤。<br />\n<br />\n文章中也提到許多離譜婚鬧事件，曾有公公藉著醉酒強吻兒媳，還有長輩自誇「老當益壯」在新娘衣服裡塞東西，還伸手捏胸、摸下體。<br />\n<br />\n此外，伴娘也成了婚鬧中無辜的受害者，不僅性侵事件頻傳，更曾鬧出人命，許多女孩害怕這樣的低俗婚鬧，即使是好姊妹結婚，也不敢去當伴娘。部分家庭為此還聘請妓女當「職業伴娘」，但她們也抱怨「職業伴娘」的錢難賺，常常胸部被抓得青一塊紫一塊，私處也被抓到流血，「好多性工作者到了現場，才發現自己是羊入虎口，即使不給錢，都不想在婚禮上多待一秒鐘」。<br />\n<br />\n「當事人覺得好笑，才算玩笑，否則，就都是純粹的惡。」文章最後呼籲，婚鬧並非婚禮的必備節目，希望所有新郎都能保護好自已的新娘。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/77J2HPkir7BTpxXMKhyPmA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.hk/aab79ed997edbfa38e5c287989f60bc3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F77J2HPkir7BTpxXMKhyPmA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.hk%2Faab79ed997edbfa38e5c287989f60bc3&h=12c6c140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SueLURPU.abfiwmeYRP7Og--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDQ1O2g9Mjkx/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.hk/cc5365bd06f9aa6cee31f900dbde440e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSueLURPU.abfiwmeYRP7Og--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDQ1O2g9Mjkx%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.hk%2Fcc5365bd06f9aa6cee31f900dbde440e&h=69406e1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05fe3b97d8f2dec61e297bbc1e1e68d3ff36182b","tid":988553,"uid":94828,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:29:40.000Z","msg":"係班死北佬先有咁變態"},{"pid":"a46bcb1da9afeef66bccff7e3818b974c8fe1075","tid":988553,"uid":51720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:30:28.000Z","msg":"某大強國地下小電影題材之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6dca6eccb76d79628a465f5e9ed64a7443d099","tid":988553,"uid":3078,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"蚹蛤蟈蜻"},{"pid":"01ce804525a1bfd1e7e9cb2dfa400db2d51bccb2","tid":988553,"uid":141151,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:34:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>長輩們卻在屋外直說「年輕人真會玩，這婚禮辦得好，熱鬧」<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"94f05cde24816b5113259f7d64ca6a5b0be07a8e","tid":988553,"uid":81113,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"六四之後冇人性"},{"pid":"798490323fd12fa72434f3b50f8e17275628bdcc","tid":988553,"uid":22701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:39:48.000Z","msg":"雞都唔肯做，班友都幾狼死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d4b6c8e74145a37cd018b2fe35be7ae91711a5","tid":988553,"uid":55019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d85e2c2025c311c6cb3d2b96b50bd392e83b9dc","tid":988553,"uid":175661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"正一生蕃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif